programRules.name: ENTO-IR-SYN Assign - 24h to time when WHO tube test conducted

programRules.description: Assign 24h to Time at which mortality was recorded when a WHO tube test was conducted

programRules.name: ENTO-IR-SYN Assign - 30min when CDC bottle assay conducted
programRules.displayName: ENTO-IR-SYN Assign - 30min when CDC bottle assay conducted
programRules.description: Assign 30min to Time at which mortality was recorded when CDC bottle assay is selected
programRules.condition: #{ENTO-IR-  Test type synergist}== 'CDC_BOTTLE_ADULTS'

programRules.name: ENTO-IR-SYN Assign - Adjusted mortalities if control mortality < 5%
programRules.displayName: ENTO-IR-SYN Assign - Adjusted mortalities if control mortality < 5%
programRules.description: Assigns adjusted mortalities if control mortality < 5%
programRules.condition: #{ENTO-IR-  Average mortality in controls} < 5

programRules.name: ENTO-IR-SYN Assign - Adjusted mortality insecticide only (control mortality => 5% and < 20%)
programRules.displayName: ENTO-IR-SYN Assign - Adjusted mortality insecticide only (control mortality => 5% and < 20%)
programRules.description: Assigns adjusted mortality to mosquitos exposed only to insecticide if control mortality => 5% and < 20%
programRules.condition: #{ENTO-IR-  Average mortality in controls} >= 5  && #{ENTO-IR-  Average mortality in controls} < 20

programRules.name: ENTO-IR-SYN Assign - Percent control mortality
programRules.displayName: ENTO-IR-SYN Assign - Percent control mortality
programRules.description: Assigns percent mortality  in control mosquitos based on number of exposed and number on dead
programRules.condition: d2:hasValue( #{ENTO-IR Number control replicate 1} )   && d2:hasValue(#{ENTO-IR Number dead control replicate 1})

programRules.name: ENTO-IR-SYN Assign - Percent mortality in insecticide only from replicates
programRules.displayName: ENTO-IR-SYN Assign - Percent mortality in insecticide only from replicates
programRules.description: Assigns percent mortality in exposed based on number of exposed and number of dead in each replicate
programRules.condition: #{ENTO-IR Number insect replicate 1} >= 0   && #{ENTO-IR Number dead insect replicate 1}  > 0

programRules.name: ENTO-IR-SYN Assign - Percent mortality in synergist and insecticide from replicates
programRules.displayName: ENTO-IR-SYN Assign - Percent mortality in synergist and insecticide from replicates
programRules.description: Assigns percent mortality in mosquitos exposed both to synergist and  insecticide based on the number of exposed and the number of dead in each replicate
programRules.condition: #{ENTO-IR Number dead sync plus insect replicate 1}>= 0 && #{ENTO-IR Number sync plus insect replicate 1}> 0

programRules.name: ENTO-IR-SYN Assign - Percent mortality in synergist only from replicates
programRules.displayName: ENTO-IR-SYN Assign - Percent mortality in synergist only from replicates
programRules.description: Assigns percent mortality in mosquitos exposed to synergist only  based on the number of exposed and the number of dead in each replicate
programRules.condition: #{ENTO-IR Number dead sync replicate 1} >= 0  && #{ENTO-IR Number sync replicate 1}> 0

programRules.name: ENTO-IR-SYN Assign - Synergist Could not be assessed
programRules.displayName: ENTO-IR-SYN Assign - Synergist Could not be assessed
programRules.description: Assign synergist involvement as could not be reliably assessed if resistance in insecticide only is >98%
programRules.condition: #{ENTO-IR-  Adjusted mortality in insecticide only replicates}>90

programRules.name: ENTO-IR-SYN Assign - Synergist Fully involved
programRules.displayName: ENTO-IR-SYN Assign - Synergist Fully involved
programRules.description: Assign synergist involvement as fully involved when adjusted mortality in insecticide only is <90 and in insecticide + synergist >= 98
programRules.condition: #{ENTO-IR-  Adjusted mortality in insecticide only replicates} < 90    && #{ENTO-IR- Adjusted mortality in synergist insecticide replicates}>= 98

programRules.name: ENTO-IR-SYN Assign - Synergist Negatively involved
programRules.displayName: ENTO-IR-SYN Assign - Synergist Negatively involved
programRules.description: Assign synergist involvement as not involved when adjusted mortality in insecticide only  replicates is <90  and  mortality in insecticide + synergist replicates is equal or lower than mortality in insecticide only replicates
programRules.condition: (#{ENTO-IR- Adjusted mortality in synergist insecticide replicates}<#{ENTO-IR-  Adjusted mortality in insecticide only replicates}) && #{ENTO-IR-  Adjusted mortality in insecticide only replicates}>0  &&  #{ENTO-IR- Adjusted mortality in synergist insecticide replicates} >0 && (#{ENTO-IR-  Adjusted mortality in insecticide only replicates}-#{ENTO-IR- Adjusted mortality in synergist insecticide replicates}>10)

programRules.name: ENTO-IR-SYN Assign - Synergist Not involved
programRules.displayName: ENTO-IR-SYN Assign - Synergist Not involved
programRules.description: Assign synergist involvement as not involved when adjusted mortality in insecticide only  replicates is <90  and  mortality in insecticide + synergist replicates is equal or lower than mortality in insecticide only replicates
programRules.condition: (#{ENTO-IR- Adjusted mortality in synergist insecticide replicates}- #{ENTO-IR-  Adjusted mortality in insecticide only replicates})<10 && (#{ENTO-IR- Adjusted mortality in synergist insecticide replicates} - #{ENTO-IR-  Adjusted mortality in insecticide only replicates})>-10   &&  d2:hasValue( #{ENTO-IR- Adjusted mortality in synergist insecticide replicates})

programRules.name: ENTO-IR-SYN Assign - Synergist Partially involved
programRules.displayName: ENTO-IR-SYN Assign - Synergist Partially involved
programRules.description: Assign synergist involvement as partially involved when adjusted mortality in insecticide only is <90 and in insecticide + synergist < 98 but adjusted mortality in insecticide+synergist is more than 10% bigger than mortality in insecticide only replicates
programRules.condition: #{ENTO-IR-  Adjusted mortality in insecticide only replicates}< 90  && #{ENTO-IR- Adjusted mortality in synergist insecticide replicates} < 98   && (#{ENTO-IR- Adjusted mortality in synergist insecticide replicates}-#{ENTO-IR-  Adjusted mortality in insecticide only replicates}) > 10

programRules.name: ENTO-IR-SYN Assign- Carbamates class
programRules.displayName: ENTO-IR-SYN Assign- Carbamates class
programRules.description: Assign carbamates class
programRules.condition: #{ENTO-IR- Insecticide}=='BEN_0.1'  || #{ENTO-IR- Insecticide}=='CAR_0.4'  || #{ENTO-IR- Insecticide}=='BEN_12.5u'  || #{ENTO-IR- Insecticide}=='PRO_10u' ||  #{ENTO-IR- Insecticide}=='PRO_0.1'

programRuleActions.data: #{ENTO-IR-  Average mortality in treatments with synergist only}
#{ENTO-IR-  Average mortality in treatments with synergist and insecticide}
#{ENTO-IR-  Average mortality in treatments with insecticide only}
100*((#{ENTO-IR-  Average mortality in treatments with insecticide only}-#{ENTO-IR-  Average mortality in controls})/(100-#{ENTO-IR-  Average mortality in controls}))
100*(#{ENTO-IR-  Average mortality in treatments with synergist insecticide}-#{ENTO-IR-  Average mortality in controls})/(100-#{ENTO-IR-  Average mortality in controls})
100*((#{ENTO-IR-  Average mortality in treatments with synergist only}-#{ENTO-IR-  Average mortality in controls})/(100-#{ENTO-IR-  Average mortality in controls}))
(#{ENTO-IR Number dead control replicate 1} + #{ENTO-IR Number dead control replicate 2})*100/(#{ENTO-IR Number control replicate 1} + #{ENTO-IR Number control replicate 2})

(#{ENTO-IR Number dead insect replicate 1} + #{ENTO-IR Number dead insect replicate 2} + #{ENTO-IR Number dead insect replicate 3} + #{ENTO-IR Number dead insect replicate 4})*100/(#{ENTO-IR Number insect replicate 1} + #{ENTO-IR Number insect replicate 2} + #{ENTO-IR Number insect replicate 3} + #{ENTO-IR Number insect replicate 4})

(#{ENTO-IR Number dead sync plus insect replicate 1} + #{ENTO-IR Number dead sync plus insect replicate 2} + #{ENTO-IR Number dead sync plus insect replicate 3} + #{ENTO-IR Number dead sync plus insect replicate 4})*100/(#{ENTO-IR Number sync plus insect replicate 1} + #{ENTO-IR Number sync plus insect replicate 2} + #{ENTO-IR Number sync plus insect replicate 3} + #{ENTO-IR Number sync plus insect replicate 4})

(#{ENTO-IR Number dead sync replicate 1} + #{ENTO-IR Number dead sync replicate 2} + #{ENTO-IR Number dead sync replicate 3} + #{ENTO-IR Number dead sync replicate 4})*100/(#{ENTO-IR Number sync replicate 1} + #{ENTO-IR Number sync replicate 2}  + #{ENTO-IR Number sync replicate 3}+ #{ENTO-IR Number sync replicate 4})
